      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo specifies standard terminology and the taxonomy of web replication and caching infrastructure as deployed today.  It introduces standard concepts, and protocols used today within this application domain.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
